33WlC1u7Z62nQkui10nI6TAj9NN6w==\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Planning test setup**\\n\\nI need to create a dedicated `RegexpMatcherFactoryTest` under the specified test directory, possibly outside the lib package. It should be public. I also have to execute the call sites to ensure everything is working as expected. Additionally, it's crucial for me to understand the dependencies and metadata involved. I'll need to read through the build.gradle file and examine the existing native unsupported pattern to get a clearer picture.\"}]}"}, {"type": "toolCall", "id": "call_wpXCZ1OnNKoBRkXHizSvnWon|fc_04d8e84f766b15940169f5663354b48193baeb151fcdc44c9b", "name": "read", "arguments": {"path": "tests/src/ant/ant/1.6/build.gradle"}}, {"type": "toolCall", "id": "call_JBGCXCYnsKZHlddpCzMrNeQ6|fc_04d8e84f766b15940169f5663354c48193885d8e757f55f490", "name": "read", "arguments": {"path": "tests/src/ant/ant/1.6/src/test/java/ant/ant/JDBCTaskTest.java"}}, {"type": "toolCall", "id": "call_1ZexSSLFoQ5pb97cre7G2Sy6|fc_04d8e84f766b15940169f5663354cc8193b6a00e9df0820dc5", "name": "read", "arguments": {"path": "metadata/ant/ant/1.6/reflect-config.json"}}, {"type": "toolCall", "id": "call_aFYwCZNswjQozd7ZoXYgKgL1|fc_04d8e84f766b15940169f5663354d48193b0c97b3d6a522de4", "name": "read", "arguments": {"path": "metadata/ant/ant/1.6/resource-config.json"}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 6919, "output": 189, "cacheRead": 7680, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 14788, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1777690160359, "responseId": "resp_04d8e84f766b15940169f56630b068819395d75bb7c322c3d9"}, "toolResults": [{"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_wpXCZ1OnNKoBRkXHizSvnWon|fc_04d8e84f766b15940169f5663354b48193baeb151fcdc44c9b", "toolName": "read", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "/*\n * Copyright and related rights waived via CC0\n *\n * You should have received a copy of the CC0 legalcode along with this\n * work. If not, see <http://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/>.\n */\nplugins {\n    id \"org.graalvm.internal.tck\"\n}\n\nString libraryVersion = tck.testedLibraryVersion.get()\n\ndependencies {\n    testImplementation \"ant:ant:$libraryVersion\"\n    testImplementation \"ant:ant-launcher:$libraryVersion\"\n    testImplementation \"ant:ant-nodeps:$libraryVersion\"\n    testImplementation \"ant:ant-trax:$libraryVersion\"\n    testImplementation \"ant:ant-xalan1:$libraryVersion\"\n    testImplementation \"ant:ant-xslp:$libraryVersion\"\n    testImplementation 'bcel:bcel:5.1'\n    testImplementation 'xml-resolver:xml-resolver:1.2'\n    testImplementation 'org.assertj:assertj-core:3.22.0'\n}\n\ntasks.withType(Test).configureEach {\n    jvmArgs '-Dfile.encoding=ISO-8859-1'\n}\n\ngraalvmNative {\n    binaries {\n        test {\n            buildArgs('-Dfile.encoding=ISO-8859-1')\n            runtimeArgs('-Dfile.encoding=ISO-8859-1')\n            runtimeArgs(\"-Djava.class.path=${sourceSets.test.runtimeClasspath.asPath}\")\n        }\n    }\n    agent {\n        defaultMode = \"conditional\"\n        modes {\n            conditional {\n                userCodeFilterPath = \"user-code-filter.json\"\n            }\n        }\n    }\n}\n"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1777690163538}, {"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_JBGCXCYnsKZHlddpCzMrNeQ6|fc_04d8e84f766b15940169f5663354c48193885d8e757f55f490", "toolName": "read", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "/*\n * Copyright and related rights waived via CC0\n *\n * You should have received a copy of the CC0 legalcode along with this\n * work. If not, see <http://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/>.\n */\npackage ant.ant;\n\nimport java.sql.Connection;\nimport java.sql.Driver;\nimport java.sql.DriverPropertyInfo;\nimport java.sql.SQLException;\nimport java.util.Properties;\nimport java.util.logging.Logger;\n\nimport org.apache.tools.ant.BuildException;\nimport org.apache.tools.ant.Project;\nimport org.apache.tools.ant.taskdefs.JDBCTask;\nimport org.apache.tools.ant.types.Path;\nimport org.graalvm.internal.tck.NativeImageSupport;\nimport org.junit.jupiter.api.Test;\n\nimport static org.assertj.core.api.Assertions.assertThat;\nimport static org.assertj.core.api.Assertions.fail;\n\npublic class JDBCTaskTest {\n    private static final String TEST_DRIVER_CLASS_NAME = NullJdbcDriver.class.getName();\n    private static final String TEST_JDBC_URL = \"jdbc:ant-test:unhandled\";\n\n    @Test\n    void loadsDriverWithSystemClassLoader() {\n        TestJDBCTask task = newConfiguredTask();\n        task.setDriver(TEST_DRIVER_CLASS_NAME);\n\n        assertDriverWasLoadedAndRejectedUrl(task);\n    }\n\n    @Test\n    void loadsDriverThroughConfiguredAntClassLoader() {\n        Project project = newProject();\n        TestJDBCTask task = newConfiguredTask(project);\n        task.setDriver(TEST_DRIVER_CLASS_NAME);\n        task.setCaching(false);\n        task.setClasspath(new Path(project, System.getProperty(\"java.class.path\")));\n\n        assertDriverWasLoadedAndRejectedUrlOrUnsupportedInNativeImage(task);\n    }\n\n    private TestJDBCTask newConfiguredTask() {\n        return newConfiguredTask(newProject());\n    }\n\n    private TestJDBCTask newConfiguredTask(Project project) {\n        TestJDBCTask task = new TestJDBCTask();\n        task.setProject(project);\n        task.setTaskName(\"jdbc-test\");\n        task.setUserid(\"user\");\n        task.setPassword(\"password\");\n        task.setUrl(TEST_JDBC_URL);\n        return task;\n    }\n\n    private Project newProject() {\n        Project project = new Project();\n        project.init();\n        return project;\n    }\n\n    private void assertDriverWasLoadedAndRejectedUrl(TestJDBCTask task) {\n        try {\n            task.openConnection();\n            fail(\"Expected JDBC connection creation to fail after loading the test driver\");\n        } catch (BuildException exception) {\n            assertThat(exception.getMessage()).contains(\"No suitable Driver\");\n        }\n    }\n\n    private void assertDriverWasLoadedAndRejectedUrlOrUnsupportedInNativeImage(TestJDBCTask task) {\n        try {\n            assertDriverWasLoadedAndRejectedUrl(task);\n        } catch (Error error) {\n            if (!NativeImageSupport.isUnsupportedFeatureError(error)) {\n                throw error;\n            }\n        }\n    }\n\n    private static final class TestJDBCTask extends JDBCTask {\n        Connection openConnection() {\n            return getConnection();\n        }\n    }\n\n    public static final class NullJdbcDriver implements Driver {\n        public NullJdbcDriver() {\n        }\n\n        public Connection connect(String url, Properties info) throws SQLException {\n            return null;\n        }\n\n        public boolean acceptsURL(String url) throws SQLException {\n            return true;\n        }\n\n        public DriverPropertyInfo[] getPropertyInfo(String url, Properties info) throws SQLException {\n            return new DriverPropertyInfo[0];\n        }\n\n        public int getMajorVersion() {\n            return 1;\n        }\n\n        public int getMinorVersion() {\n            return 0;\n        }\n\n        public boolean jdbcCompliant() {\n            return false;\n        }\n\n        public Logger getParentLogger() {\n            return Logger.getLogger(NullJdbcDriver.class.getName());\n        }\n    }\n}\n"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1777690163538}, {"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_1ZexSSLFoQ5pb97cre7G2Sy6|fc_04d8e84f766b15940169f5663354cc8193b6a00e9df0820dc5", "toolName": "read", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "ENOENT: no such file or directory, access '/home/vjovanov/c/forge/forge10/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/local_repositories/forge_worktrees/2392-e88107e6/metadata/ant/ant/1.6/reflect-config.json'"}], "details": {}, "isError": true, "timestamp": 1777690163538}, {"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_aFYwCZNswjQozd7ZoXYgKgL1|fc_04d8e84f766b15940169f5663354d48193b0c97b3d6a522de4", "toolName": "read", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "ENOENT: no such file or directory, access '/home/vjovanov/c/forge/forge10/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/local_repositories/forge_worktrees/2392-e88107e6/metadata/ant/ant/1.6/resource-config.json'"}], "details": {}, "isError": true, "timestamp": 1777690163540}]}
